    <!-- Tutorial Screen -->
    <string name="tutorial_step_1">1. Click Play then select a Category and finally a Game to play.</string>
    <string name="tutorial_step_2">2. Once you are sure of your decision, hit Play.</string>
    <string name="tutorial_step_3">
        Important: Once you\'ve started a game, exiting an app will restart your game and cause you to
        lose progress.
    </string>
    <string name="tutorial_step_4">
        3. Read and answer the question or identify the molecule shown.
           You can rotate the molecule with your finger, as well as use pinch-to-zoom.
    </string>
    <string name="tutorial_step_5">Correct answers gain you points, incorrect answers cost you points.</string>
    <string name="tutorial_step_6">
        Finish before the timer runs out. Finishing faster will gain you extra points and
        an opportunity to get within the top 10!
